e of the American film star  John Wayne  (  1907–79 )."]},{"name":"Marcia","meanings":["Often used as a feminine equivalent of   Mark  , but in fact a feminine form of <i>Marcius</i>, itself a derivative of   Marcus .  One  St Marcia  is commemorated in a group with Felix, Luciolus, Fortunatus, and others; another with Zenais, Cyria, and Valeria; and a third with Ariston, Crescentian, Eutychian, Urban, Vitalis, Justus, Felicissimus, Felix, and Symphorosa. None is individually very famous."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mary Ferress was born in 1405, in Waltham, Kent, England, United Kingdom. She married Henry Horne in 1428, in Waltham, Kent, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in 1434, in her hometown, at the age of 29."},"et":{"1405–1434":"1405–1434","1400–1434":"1400–1434","1434–1497":"1434–1497","1434":"1434","1400":"1400","1497":"1497","Abt 1434":"umbes 1434","1428":"1428","1405":"1405","Waltham, Kent, England":"Waltham, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Waltham, City of Canterbury, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Waltham, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1405–1434":"1405–1434","1400–1434":"1400–1434","1434–1497":"1434–1497","1434":"1434","1400":"1400","1497":"1497","Abt 1434":"noin 1434","1428":"1428","1405":"1405","Waltham, Kent, England":"Waltham, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Waltham, City of Canterbury, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Waltham, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1405–1434":"1405–1434","1400–1434":"1400–1434","1434–1497":"1434–1497","1434":"1434","1400":"1400","1497":"1497","Abt 1434":"environ 1434","1428":"1428","1405":"1405","Waltham, Kent, England":"Waltham, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Waltham, City of Canterbury, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Waltham, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mary Ferress est née en 1405, à Waltham, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Henry Horne en 1428, à Waltham, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1